Unless you have a super bandwidth, please jump off torrents until you're left with only a couple and continue seeding this one.

As an uploader you're responsible for letting people leech from you.

After you're done 100%, you're free to go elsewhere and leave the seeding to ppl who's already snatched your torrent... and of course, they should stay on until reaching a factor of 1:1 share ratio.

If ppl. got used to do that there'd be not much hassle amongst users here on PB :-) It's all about sharing, ain't it..?
